Exercise 3

Exercise 4

ggplot(SNPs, aes(x=chromosome, fill =  genotype)) +
  geom_bar(position = "fill")

Exercise 5

ggplot(SNPs, aes(x=chromosome, fill =  genotype)) +
  geom_bar(position = "dodge")

Exercise 6

ggplot(SNPs, aes(x=chromosome, fill =  genotype)) +
  geom_bar(position = "dodge") +
  facet_wrap(~genotype)
